description: To keep their secret weapon out of the hands of the invading Broodwarriors, the heroes of Trelkas stage a final resistance and send a powerful package out through the universe -- to Earth, where a young boy will use it to protect his own world when the Broodwarriors come calling.

description: A heaping helping of timeless tales of Your Friendly Neighborhood Spider-Man! First, Mary Jane takes center stage as she teams up with She-Hulk, Hellcat, Marvel Girl, and some other lovely ladies to take on The Enchantress! Next, see what happens when an old television program that features Spider-Man and ARANA (with guest appearances by Spider-Ham and the Spider-Mobile) returns to haunt Spider-Girl! Plus, Peter Parker - a.k.a. Spider-Man - is the last survivor of the secret ninja group known as the Spider-Clan... or so he thought. But when Peter is attacked at the gravesite of his Uncle Ben, he goes on a quest to learn the truth behind his origins - and he won't like what he learns! Collects King-Size Spider-Man Summer Special #1, Spider-Man Family #1, Amazing Spider-Man Magazine, and Spider-Man Family Featuring Spider-Clan #1

description: In the year 2029, astronaut/pilot Leo Davidson is in for an adventure -- and a nightmare -- unlike anything else. While conducting vital research in space on apes enhanced with human DNA, the crew of the starship Oberon investigates a strange anomaly. Pericles -- one of the genetically enhanced chimps trained as a pilot by Leo -- is given the task of investigating the odd occurrence in a prototype space pod. When Pericles disappears, Leo disregards all orders and heads out to find his friend. Once caught in the grip of the anomaly, Leo is pulled into a time and place that he could never imagine...the PLANET OF THE APES! What he experiences there is almost beyond his belief: a world where gorillas and chimps are the dominant species... a world where humans struggle to survive in the wild beneath the heel of ape rule. With the help of a sympathetic chimpanzee activist named Ari, Leo leads the effort to evade the advancing gorilla army led by the sinister Thade. And maybe, just maybe, Leo will make it back home...if he survives the war he's started.

description: While the memories of the past of the Praetorian Scipio and Atticus Kane come to mind , the first evidences against Imperium Enterprise start coming to light. But the Attorney Klint obtains that the Agency Alfa suspends its investigation on the construction company that is rebuilding the city ... An unexpected help, though, could come from Mary Jane Lamarr, former wife of Kane.
name: Imperium

description: Still reeling from the startling truth, an angry Steve 'Marineman' Ocean heads back to Marine Base Alpha to confront his father and Admiral Brookes before returning to the 'Leviathan' for the final showdown! Don't miss it!
name: Chapter Six: A Matter Of Life And Depth

description: In the German universities, someone commits a bloody murder in order to gain possession of an ancient book of black magic, the Grimorio ‚ÄúDe Profundis‚Äù, which centuries ago was split up into four parts because it was so very dangerous. Under the disguise of a professor of vampirology, Harlan Draka investigates in Freiburg, with the help of his friend professor Milius. He thus comes up against the Keeper of the last part of the Grimorio, who has an attractive feminine appearance, but the same can‚Äôt be said about his adversaries, whom he also bumps into!
name: Dalle tenebre

description: Tesla returns to Berlin, the city of her youth, in search of her past life and her great love of past times, a rebel singer and songwriter who is dying of AIDS. Tesla and Harlan fight against Shrek, the Master who handed her over to Gorka thirty years before. And at their side there is a strange friend-cum-foe, the beautiful Lamiah, risen from her tomb to avenge Shrek.
name: Lamiah

description:
Paris, Montparnasse. In Rue Delambre there is a house of horrors. Along with Victor, a new friend who is a bizarre poet and chansonnier in love with the hibernating vampire Araxe, Harlan Draka comes up against the mystery of the mansion that has a curse on it, built in the eighteenth century by the demoniacal architect Tenardier.

Dampyr travels to Paris, where he meets Victor, the guardian of the sleep of Araxe, Mistress of the Night in "hibernation", who asks to help him defeat a arch-vampire that wants to dominate his whole race. Verdier, the arch-vampire, has become almost an integral part of a house built by an architect-alchemist specifically to accommodate it.
name: Casa di sangue

description: Kurjak returns to his land where the recent conflicts have caused mayhem, only to discover that peace has not yet been restored and that Nadjia, his first love, was killed with the complicity of his perfidious rival Mathias. While contending with ancient feuds among Slavic families and chemical experiments conducted on human guinea pigs, Harlan and Tesla are staunchly on Kurjak‚Äôs side in the struggle to save his village.
name: Nemesis

description: In Prague, in the district of Mal√† Strana, Nikolaus wants to acquire wealth and supreme knowledge by completing an alchemist experiment that was started centuries before by the adventurer Sendivogius: it‚Äôs the plan to purify a ‚Äúdybbuk‚Äù, a soul lost in a time warp. But Nergal, the head of Hell‚Äôs secret police, does not agree, and Harlan and Caleb must intervene to save their friend-cum-foe from a fate worse than death...
name: Anima persa

description: In 1946, in Nuremberg, little Ann Jurging escapes from the dangerous dancing school run by Helena Morkov. More than fifty years on, on an island with a curse on it in the middle of the Aegean Sea, Ann and Dampyr face the Queen of Witches , her ‚ÄúFuries‚Äù and their monstrous followers‚Ä¶
name: L'isola della strega

description: On the mountains of the Caucasus , the centuries-old hatred between the occupying foreign overlords and the local population develops into bitter modern warfare. Among the ruins of Djovkhar, the capital, and in the nearby villages, the OM ‚Äì soldiers of the special squads ‚Äì indiscriminately slaughter partisans and civilians without distinction. But in the midst of all this barbarism, the front line doctors of the International Medical Team try to save lives. And in the underground passages beneath the destroyed city, ‚ÄúThe vampires of Djovkhar‚Äù keep watch in the darkness...
name: I ribelli

description:
In the fabulous seventies, an aeroplane crashed into the swamps of the Mississippi Delta killing or mutilating the members of the Swampy Lizards rock band while they were at the peak of their success. Today their legend has been revived and their music still echoes in the swamp... amid screams of death and terror!

Harlan and Kurjak are on duty in Mississippi on the trail of a master of the night who has assumed the role of a demon voodoo, Legba (or Maitre Carrefour), the "Lord of the crossroads." One legend has it that Robert Johnson, famous bluesman of the thirties, who disappeared in mysterious ways, sold his soul to this demon. Helped in their quest by an old man and a young musician (the latter, who lives in the myth of Johnson, would like to retrace the career) our heroes face yet another opponent in a long and intricate adventure where horror and music are intertwined.
name: Nato nella palude

description: On the tracks of Legba, the Master who has transmogrified the Swamp Lizards into non-dead, Harlan and Kurjak and their friends find themselves involved in solving an enigma from the history of blues‚Ä¶ Why did Robert Johnson die? They have to uncover what really happened in this old ‚Äúwho-dun-it‚Äù from the Nineteen-Thirties and avenge the legendary bluesman, as well as shaking off the entire police force of the State of Mississippi who, of course, are in hot pursuit!
name: Delta Blues

description: Frank Aaron is a police officer who struggles with the curse of being a werewolf. As he investigates the brutal murder of the Mayor's family, he notices claw marks, saliva, and animal hair at the crime scene, leading him to wonder if he might be responsible. But in the course of his investigation, he discovers that there is another werewolf in town, and he is forced to use the abilities of his feral side to track down his counterpart and solve the mystery of the murder.
name: Lethal Instinct TPB

description: Playing their largest concert in their hometown, metal band and reformed monster hunters ‚ÄúSubliminal Torment‚Äù and their fans are attacked by the worst creatures they‚Äôve ever faced. After the monsters slaughter the fans in homage to a previous encounter, the band is left to take the fall. * In heavy metal, there are dangers that surpass mosh pits and diseased groupies. * Rap and country ain't the only music genres that has to live out their lyrics...

Romance comics have an outdated and cheesy stigma about them, but once they played a large role within comic history. Within the third phase of the golden era (1948 to 1954) comic readership was at an all time high, read by both men and women, and romance comics were one of the five genres that kept comic readership diverse. In an attempt to bring more diversity back to comics, Arcana is proud to present the Amour Anthology!
